data.description: Welcome to your private oasis! This stunning two-story home is nestled on a sprawling 3.9-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Located in a serene setting, with a small creek meandering through the back yard, this property promises a lifestyle of serenity and natural beauty.    As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by a large front porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the peaceful surroundings. The main level features a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace, ideal for gathering with family and friends. The adjacent kitchen boasts modern appliances, quartz countertops, ample cabinet space, a breakfast nook with tile throughout the kitchen. The first floor offers two bedrooms and a full size bathroom, along with a large master suite and ensuite bathroom.    In addition to the main living areas, this home also offers a large sunroom, providing a bright and airy space to relax and soak in the views of the surrounding landscape. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or unwinding with a good book, the sunroom is sure to become one of your favorite spots in the house.    Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms, a flex space and another full bathroom provide plenty of space for family members or guests.  Outside, the expansive backyard beckons you to explore and unwind. Relax on the deck overlooking the scenic creek, listen to the soothing sounds of nature. The possibilities are endless in this picturesque outdoor space.
